room_title: Escape room "Black Hat" by The Encrypted Escape in Green Bay
room_address: 1390 Bellevue St, Suite 105 Green Bay, WI 54311
room_description: In the old west, money is hard to come by. When times get tough, a person must be even tougher. You’ve heard of a safe full of treasure, perhaps enough treasure that a man could live like a king for the rest of his days, nestled in a community not far from yours. Your gang has decided that it’s time to take that treasure for yourselves. To do so, you must set into motion a plan so daring and risky, it’s unlike any other job you’ve done before.
